# Cursor Rules for this project

## Git Commit Rules

- NEVER add "Co-authored-by" trailers to commit messages
- NEVER include Cursor or any AI assistant as a co-author in git commits
- Keep commit messages clean and only include the actual commit content
- Do not add any attribution to AI assistance in commit messages

## Code Style

- Follow conventional commit format for all commits
- Use appropriate prefixes: feat:, fix:, refactor:, etc.
- Keep commit messages concise but descriptive
